@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1/yolo

### Submit Job
# @name submitJob
POST {{baseUrl}}/predict?fields=boxes,masks,names,keypoints
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": "https://t4.ftcdn.net/jpg/02/24/86/95/360_F_224869519_aRaeLneqALfPNBzg0xxMZXghtvBXkfI.jpg"
